### Pull gacha
POST https://api.example.com/api/gacha/pull
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "bannerTag": "season1-global",
  "cost": 160
}

### Resolve downed character (use soul stone)
POST https://api.example.com/api/roster/{{characterId}}/revive
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "consumeSoulStone": true
}

### Finalize permadeath (system or admin-triggered worker)
POST https://api.example.com/internal/permadeath/finalize
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

{
  "nowUtc": "2026-04-16T00:00:00Z"
}

### Get live pool top rarity
GET https://api.example.com/api/pool/live?minRarity=8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Matchmaking queue
POST https://api.example.com/api/matchmaking/enqueue
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "teamCharacterIds": [
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
  ]
}
